      <p>a next-generation software system. workers. triggers. functions.</p>
    </div>
    <div class="foot-col">
      <h5>developers</h5>
      <ul>
        <li><a href="/docs">docs</a></li>
        <li><a href="/docs/quickstart">quickstart</a></li>
        <li><a href="/blog/">blog</a></li>
        <li><a href="https://github.com/iii-hq/iii" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">github</a></li>
      </ul>
    </div>
    <div class="foot-col">
      <h5>contact</h5>
      <ul>
        <li><a href="https://discord.gg/motia" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">discord</a></li>
        <li><a href="https://x.com/iiidevs" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">twitter / X</a></li>
        <li>
          <a href="https://www.linkedin.com/company/iii-dev" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">linkedin</a>
        </li>
